<h1>Criminological Information Service</h1>
<p>Goal and task of the Criminological Information Service (FID Kriminologie) is to supply the supra-regional scientific community with criminological special literature, as well as with other information relevant to research and the subject of criminology as a whole. This is a project established in cooperation between the Institute for Criminology and the university library of the University of Tübingen and sponsored by the German research foundation.</p>

<h1>About the FID Criminology</h1>
<p>The FID is mainly focused on the task to provide the scientific community with literature and other subject-relevant Information about criminology.</p>

